<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>
        Agustin Lleras' Personal Site
    </title>
    <meta name="description" content="">
    <meta name="author" content="Agustin Lleras">

    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Work+Sans" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.fontawesome.com/releases/v5.1.0/css/all.css" integrity="sha384-lKuwvrZot6UHsBSfcMvOkWwlCMgc0TaWr+30HWe3a4ltaBwTZhyTEggF5tJv8tbt" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/normalize.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/style.css">
    <script type="text/javascript" src="assets/js/main.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="container header">
            <a href="#" class="logo">
                <img src="assets/logo.png" />
            </a>
            <ul class="navbar-links">
                <li class='navbar-item'>
                    <a href='#'>Home</a>
                </li>
                <li class='navbar-item'>
                    <a href='#projects'>Projects</a>
                </li>
                <li class='navbar-item'>
                    <a href='#about'>About</a>
                </li>
                <div class='clearfix'></div>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </nav>
    <div class="container greeter">
        <h1 class="greeter-header">Hey! Agustin here.</h1>
        <span class="greeter-subtext">
            {MD}
            My full name? **Agustin Lleras**; and yes, you can pronounce it like Augustine.

            I am a super great person with interests in **Node.js** and **front-end** web development.
            {/MD}
        </span>
        <hr>
    </div>
    <div class="container main">
        <section id="about">
            <h5 class="section-header">
                <span class="section-header-text">About me</span>
            </h5>
            <div class="section-content">
                {MD}This is a paragraph containing **my own information** in short sentences. I am 21 and this is my first attempt at a portfolio website. Many remakes will come, probably, as I'm always hungry for perfection.

                I was born in Venezuela and studied Telecommunications Engineering up until the point I had to leave my country. Pretty cool huh?{/MD}
            </div>
        </section>
        <section id="projects">
            <h5 class="section-header">
                <span class="section-header-text">Projects</span>
            </h5>

            <div class="projectFlexbox half-wider">
                <% for(var i=0; i< projects.length; i++) {%>
                    <div class="projectCard">
                        <div class="projectCard__image">
                            <img src="<%= projects[i].imgPath %>" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="projectCard__content">
                            <span class="projectCard__title">
                                <%= projects[i].title %>
                            </span>
                            <span class="projectCard__description">
                                    <%= projects[i].description %>
                            </span>
                            <hr class="projectCard__innerSeparator" />
                            <h2 class="projectCard__tagsTitle">Tags</h2>
                            <ul class="tagList">
                                <% for(var j=0; j< projects[i].tags.length; j++) {%>
                                    <li class="tagList__tag"><%= projects[i].tags[j] %></li>
                                <% } %>
                            </ul>
                            <a href="<%= projects[i].link %>" class="projectCard__button button button-primary">View</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
    <a href="#" id="goUpButton">
        <i class="goUpButton__arrow fa fa-chevron-up" aria-hidden="true"></i>
    </a>
</body>
</html>